## Interview

### What to say

1. Why do you want to work here?
talk about company culture, the mission, and position and why it lines up with your goals and asperations.
Get excited about the opportunity!

2. When you're asked about the last place of employment?
Speak positivly; not the time to speak on negative aspects!

3. Where do you see yourself in 5 years?
Answer in the perspective of still working at the company, only!

## DevOps
Design, implement, and maintain systems involving REST APIs, websocket APIs, databases, caching systems, mailing systems, queueing systems, networked storage, logging systems, cloud orchestration, and more
